Looks good. @mgaido91 .
Could you add more to be complete? For example, `ByteType`, `DecimalType`, `DateType`, `BinaryType`, `StructType`?
`StructType ` is already present. I added the others but `BinaryType` because the array of bytes as toString returns just a reference, so it makes little sense to add it IMO. Thanks.
